Package: ompr.roi
Type: Package
Title: A Solver for 'ompr' that Uses the R Optimization Infrastructure ('ROI')
Version: 0.4.1.9001
Authors@R: person("Dirk", "Schumacher", email = "mail@dirk-schumacher.net",
            role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: A solver for 'ompr' based on the R Optimization Infrastructure ('ROI').
  The package makes all solvers in 'ROI' available to solve 'ompr' models. See the
  ompr website/package docs for examples on how to use it.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
URL: https://github.com/dirkschumacher/ompr.roi
BugReports: https://github.com/dirkschumacher/ompr.roi/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
  ROI,
  ompr (>= 0.5.0.9001)
Suggests:
  testthat,
  magrittr,
  ROI.plugin.glpk
ByteCompile: Yes
